survey_response.review_text: Having a dentist in the neighbourhood, who has an excellent well  , friendly staff and a mobile booster is always a boon. My visit to the clinic was for  my child cleaning and was really impressed by Dr. Pritee Ray treatment and time savers to explain how to keep the teeth healthy. I surely recommend to visit 'the dentist' and console Dr Pritee Ray for your dental hygiene.
Dr Preeti is a very decent person. Her work is recommended in all perspectives. She listens to the problem very carefully and then operates. I would like to recommend her for dental issues.

Highly skilled and treated with complete patience.
Highly recommended for any dental issues.
No wait time as well.

She is kind and a patient doctor. She will listen to you and explain everything to you in detail. What I liked best about her was the way she calmed me down during such long and frustrating sessions as I had multiple issues and the way she went above and beyond her duties. Thank you so much for your kindness.

Doctor Pritee was very supportive and showed lot of patience in handling. She had to wait multiple times for me during the extraction and give me short breaks but she was happy to wait. I felt like some one my own was helping me out.

Thank you doctor

Doctor Pritee is nice doctor. She explained the issue in detail. I was always scared of visiting dentist but after having treatment with Dr Pritee that fear has gone. Have done the scaling first time and no pain/issues after that. Strongly recommend Dr Pritee for any dental issue.

Dr Pritee was quick in analysing the issue and treating the same resulting in immediate relief from the pain I was going through. Her treatment was great and her friendly follow-ups was super warm. She was kind enough to attend to my issues during this pandemic and adjust the time to suit my requirements.

Her caring and patience makes the battle half won. Patient is within a comfort zone under her confident diagnosis. I had a good experience for my mother's RCT. She even enquired about my mother teeth status after her treatment. This is one of the rarest approach I found made by any doctor. I would like to recommend her for anyone.

Was upto speed in a matter of minutes after explaining my condition to her and got I fixed in 2 sitting. And was both the sittings we done in mere 30 minutes. Definitely give her a try. You wouldn't be disappointed. Have already recommended her to my friends regarding dental works. I'd suggest you to approach her.
